Class ReadOnlyViewStore.ReadOnlyMaterializedViewVersion

All Implemented Interfaces:

Enclosing class:
ReadOnlyViewStore
public static class ReadOnlyViewStore.ReadOnlyMaterializedViewVersion extends ReadOnlyStore.ReadOnlyVersion
A read only Version representation of a materialized view for consumers (e.g. DVC client). Any view specific version properties will be overwritten here and provided by the corresponding MaterializedView.
